      <title>台湾官员称中国将加大拘押力度以压制赖昌星</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/china-to-step-up-detentions-to-squeeze-lai-taiwan-officials-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾高级安全官员称，中国可能会根据一项针对“台独”支持者的法律拘捕更多台湾人，以向新总统施加压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/china-to-step-up-detentions-to-squeeze-lai-taiwan-officials-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 05:49:04 GMT</pubDate>
